# Local-only memory files (Anqi's project context + workflow
# preferences + session logs). Bootstrap-loaded by the dev
# environment, not synced via this repo's remote. See
# workspace .gitignore for the same pattern.
#
# If you want to share a curated subset, copy to a tracked
# file (e.g. CONTEXT.md) and commit that instead.
MEMORY.md
memory.md
memory/*.md
